<!doctype html>
<html lang="<%= lang %>">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <link rel="icon" href="/favicon.svg" type="image/svg+xml" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <%- include('partials/theme-bootstrap-head', { defaultTheme: 'light' }) %>
    <title>Статус викладача</title>
    <link
      href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css"
      rel="stylesheet"
      integrity="sha384-QWTKZyjpPEjISv5WaRU9OFeRpok6YctnYmDr5pNlyT2bRjXh0JMhjY6hW+ALEwIH"
      crossorigin="anonymous"
    />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/design-system.css?v=<%= encodeURIComponent(String(appVersion || '0.0.0')) %>" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/studerria-ui.css?v=<%= encodeURIComponent(String(appVersion || '0.0.0')) %>" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/dynamic-bg.css?v=<%= encodeURIComponent(String(appVersion || '0.0.0')) %>" />
    <style>
      :root {
        --accent: #3b82f6;
        --accent-dark: #2563eb;
        --card-radius: 28px;
        --glass-border-dark: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.14);
        --glass-border-light: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.08);
        --glass-bg-dark: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.07);
        --glass-bg-light: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.72);
      }

      body {
        min-height: 100vh;
        font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "SF Pro Text", "SF Pro Display",
          "Helvetica Neue", "Inter", Arial, sans-serif;
      }

      body.theme-light {
        background:
          radial-gradient(1200px 800px at 20% 10%, rgba(147, 197, 253, 0.28), transparent 60%),
          radial-gradient(1000px 700px at 90% 20%, rgba(196, 181, 253, 0.28), transparent 60%),
          linear-gradient(135deg, #edf3ff 0%, #eef6ff 48%, #f8f4ff 100%);
        color: #0f172a;
      }

      body.theme-dark {
        background:
          radial-gradient(1200px 800px at 15% 10%, rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.26), transparent 60%),
          radial-gradient(1000px 700px at 80% 20%, rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.22), transparent 60%),
          linear-gradient(160deg, #050508 0%, #11091a 48%, #18122a 100%);
        color: #f8fafc;
      }

      .pending-shell {
        padding-top: 10px;
        padding-bottom: 48px;
      }

      .pending-card {
        position: relative;
        isolation: isolate;
        overflow: hidden;
        max-width: 560px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 28px;
        border-radius: var(--card-radius);
        backdrop-filter: blur(22px) saturate(1.18);
        transition: background 220ms ease, border-color 220ms ease, box-shadow 220ms ease;
      }

      .pending-card::before {
        content: "";
        position: absolute;
        inset: 0;
        background:
          linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.18), transparent 44%),
          radial-gradient(circle at top right, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.14), transparent 36%);
        pointer-events: none;
      }

      body.theme-dark .pending-card {
        background: var(--glass-bg-dark);
        border: 1px solid var(--glass-border-dark);
        box-shadow: 0 22px 56px rgba(5, 8, 20, 0.52), inset 0 1px 0 rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06);
      }

      body.theme-light .pending-card {
        background: var(--glass-bg-light);
        border: 1px solid var(--glass-border-light);
        box-shadow: 0 18px 46px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.12), inset 0 1px 0 rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.78);
      }

      .pending-kicker {
        position: relative;
        z-index: 1;
        display: inline-flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 8px;
        margin-bottom: 14px;
        padding: 7px 12px;
        border-radius: 999px;
        font-size: 0.78rem;
        font-weight: 600;
        letter-spacing: 0.04em;
        text-transform: uppercase;
      }

      body.theme-dark .pending-kicker {
        background: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.42);
        border: 1px solid rgba(148, 163, 184, 0.24);
        color: rgba(226, 232, 240, 0.8);
      }

      body.theme-light .pending-kicker {
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.82);
        border: 1px solid rgba(148, 163, 184, 0.18);
        color: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.68);
      }

      .pending-hero {
        position: relative;
        z-index: 1;
        display: grid;
        place-items: center;
        min-height: 180px;
        margin-bottom: 18px;
      }

      .pending-hero__orb {
        position: relative;
        display: grid;
        place-items: center;
        width: 132px;
        height: 132px;
        border-radius: 40px;
        backdrop-filter: blur(18px) saturate(1.22);
        animation: pending-orb-breathe 4.8s ease-in-out infinite;
        box-shadow:
          0 22px 38px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.16),
          inset 0 1px 0 rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.48);
      }

      .pending-hero__orb::before,
      .pending-hero__orb::after {
        content: "";
        position: absolute;
        inset: 10px;
        border-radius: 32px;
        pointer-events: none;
      }

      .pending-hero__orb::before {
        background: linear-gradient(145deg, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.26), transparent 52%);
      }

      .pending-hero__orb::after {
        inset: -18px;
        border-radius: 52px;
        opacity: 0.55;
        filter: blur(10px);
        animation: pending-halo-drift 5.6s ease-in-out infinite;
      }

      body.theme-dark .pending-hero__orb {
        background: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.42);
        border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.14);
      }

      body.theme-dark .pending-hero__orb::after {
        background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(96, 165, 250, 0.22), transparent 68%);
      }

      body.theme-light .pending-hero__orb {
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.76);
        border: 1px solid rgba(148, 163, 184, 0.16);
      }

      body.theme-light .pending-hero__orb::after {
        background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(129, 140, 248, 0.16), transparent 68%);
      }

      .pending-hero__emoji {
        position: relative;
        z-index: 1;
        font-size: 3.55rem;
        line-height: 1;
        transform-origin: center;
        animation: pending-emoji-float 3.6s ease-in-out infinite;
        filter: drop-shadow(0 12px 20px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.12));
      }

      .pending-hero__dot {
        position: absolute;
        display: inline-flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        min-width: 38px;
        height: 38px;
        padding: 0 12px;
        border-radius: 999px;
        font-size: 1rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        line-height: 1;
        letter-spacing: 0.08em;
        backdrop-filter: blur(14px);
        animation: pending-dot-pulse 2.4s ease-in-out infinite;
      }

      .pending-hero__dot--one {
        top: 18px;
        left: calc(50% - 94px);
        animation-delay: -0.9s;
      }

      .pending-hero__dot--two {
        right: calc(50% - 92px);
        bottom: 20px;
        animation-delay: -1.6s;
      }

      body.theme-dark .pending-hero__dot {
        background: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.46);
        border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.12);
        color: rgba(226, 232, 240, 0.7);
      }

      body.theme-light .pending-hero__dot {
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
        border: 1px solid rgba(148, 163, 184, 0.16);
        color: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.48);
      }

      .pending-title {
        position: relative;
        z-index: 1;
        margin: 0;
        font-size: clamp(1.85rem, 4vw, 2.45rem);
        font-weight: 700;
        letter-spacing: -0.03em;
      }

      .pending-copy {
        position: relative;
        z-index: 1;
        margin: 14px 0 0;
        font-size: 0.98rem;
        line-height: 1.6;
      }

      body.theme-dark .pending-copy {
        color: rgba(226, 232, 240, 0.8);
      }

      body.theme-light .pending-copy {
        color: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.66);
      }

      .pending-status {
        position: relative;
        z-index: 1;
        display: inline-flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 10px;
        margin-top: 18px;
        padding: 10px 14px;
        border-radius: 999px;
        font-size: 0.9rem;
        font-weight: 600;
      }

      .pending-status::before {
        content: "";
        width: 9px;
        height: 9px;
        border-radius: 999px;
        flex: 0 0 auto;
      }

      .pending-status--pending::before {
        background: #60a5fa;
        box-shadow: 0 0 0 6px rgba(96, 165, 250, 0.12);
      }

      .pending-status--rejected::before {
        background: #f87171;
        box-shadow: 0 0 0 6px rgba(248, 113, 113, 0.12);
      }

      body.theme-dark .pending-status {
        background: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.42);
        border: 1px solid rgba(148, 163, 184, 0.2);
      }

      body.theme-light .pending-status {
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.82);
        border: 1px solid rgba(148, 163, 184, 0.16);
      }

      .pending-actions {
        position: relative;
        z-index: 1;
        display: grid;
        gap: 10px;
        margin-top: 24px;
      }

      .btn {
        border-radius: 14px;
        padding: 0.85rem 1rem;
        font-weight: 600;
      }

      .btn-primary {
        background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--accent) 0%, var(--accent-dark) 100%);
        border: none;
      }

      body.theme-dark .btn-outline-secondary {
        color: #e2e8f0;
        border-color: rgba(148, 163, 184, 0.55);
        background: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.34);
      }

      body.theme-dark .btn-outline-secondary:hover {
        color: #f8fafc;
        border-color: rgba(148, 163, 184, 0.82);
        background: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.18);
      }

      @keyframes pending-orb-breathe {
        0%, 100% {
          transform: translateY(0) scale(1);
        }
        50% {
          transform: translateY(-4px) scale(1.035);
        }
      }

      @keyframes pending-emoji-float {
        0%, 100% {
          transform: translateY(0) rotate(-2deg);
        }
        50% {
          transform: translateY(-6px) rotate(2deg);
        }
      }

      @keyframes pending-halo-drift {
        0%, 100% {
          transform: scale(0.96);
          opacity: 0.42;
        }
        50% {
          transform: scale(1.06);
          opacity: 0.72;
        }
      }

      @keyframes pending-dot-pulse {
        0%, 100% {
          transform: translateY(0) scale(0.96);
          opacity: 0.55;
        }
        50% {
          transform: translateY(-4px) scale(1.04);
          opacity: 1;
        }
      }

      @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
        .pending-hero__orb,
        .pending-hero__orb::after,
        .pending-hero__emoji,
        .pending-hero__dot {
          animation: none;
        }
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body class="studerria-theme theme-light page-teacher-pending page-local-topbar">
    <%- include('partials/theme-bootstrap-body') %>
    <%- include('partials/dynamic-bg') %>
    <%- include('partials/topbar', { role, username, t, activePage: 'teacher-pending', currentPath }) %>
    <main class="page-container pending-shell">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="pending-card">
          <% if (status === 'rejected') { %>
            <div class="pending-kicker">Teacher request</div>
            <div class="pending-hero" aria-hidden="true">
              <div class="pending-hero__orb">
                <span class="pending-hero__emoji">↩️</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <h1 class="pending-title">Потрібне оновлення вибору</h1>
            <p class="pending-copy">Вашу заявку відхилено. Оновіть перелік дисциплін і подайте викладацький маршрут повторно.</p>
            <div class="pending-status pending-status--rejected">Заявку відхилено</div>
            <div class="pending-actions">
              <a class="btn btn-primary" href="/teacher/subjects">Змінити дисципліни</a>
              <a class="btn btn-outline-secondary" href="/profile">Профіль</a>
            </div>
          <% } else { %>
            <div class="pending-hero" aria-hidden="true">
              <span class="pending-hero__dot pending-hero__dot--one">···</span>
              <div class="pending-hero__orb">
                <span class="pending-hero__emoji">⏳</span>
              </div>
              <span class="pending-hero__dot pending-hero__dot--two">···</span>
            </div>
            <h1 class="pending-title">Очікуємо підтвердження</h1>
            <p class="pending-copy">Заявка на викладача вже на розгляді адміністратора. Після підтвердження доступ до викладацького простору відкриється автоматично.</p>
            <div class="pending-status pending-status--pending">Статус: очікує підтвердження</div>
            <div class="pending-actions">
              <a class="btn btn-outline-secondary" href="/profile">Профіль</a>
              <form method="POST" action="/logout">
                <button class="btn btn-outline-secondary w-100" type="submit">Вийти</button>
              </form>
            </div>
          <% } %>
        </div>
      </div>
    </main>
    <script src="/js/design-system.js" defer></script>
    <script src="/js/dynamic-bg.js?v=<%= encodeURIComponent(String(appVersion || '0.0.0')) %>" defer></script>
  </body>
</html>
